title: Santa Cruz Night Owl Cruzer by Jeremy Fish
description:
Here at Santa Cruz Skateboards we don't suggest shredding at night while intoxicated... but if you do, do it on the Night Owl Cruzer designed by Jeremy Fish. Features foot-activated head lights and tail lights, 66mm cruzer wheels that light up when you roll, and even glows in the dark!

Check out the Night Owl Cruzer here:
http://bit.ly/nightowlcruzer
